title: DDFP 614: Week 10 Red Challenge Flag picks & Notre Dame vs. Miami
itunes:title: DDFP 614: Week 10 Red Challenge Flag picks & Notre Dame vs. Miami
description:
Dave Dameshek is joined by Matt “Money” Smith and Cynthia Frelund to discuss the college football playoffs seeding (16:30), as well as break down the upcoming matchup between Notre Dame and Miami (14:45). Also, in the start of a music-related series, the fellas and Cynthia reveal what their walkup song would be on the baseball diamond (34:10). Then, EmmaVP reads her Week 10 "TV Guide" teen drama edition game previews for the guys to break down and make their Red Challenge Flag picks (42:35). Plus, tune in for the return of Surprise Game Show (22:17)!

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
